Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer 7 Kiora Crescent, Yennora for lease. This recently DA approved facility is now under construction and benefits from the below features; 

- Corporate office: 686sqm* 
- Warehouse: 12,415sqm* 
- Total building area: 13,100sqm* 
- Site area: 26,660sqm* 
- Ground works have commenced
- Due for completion mid 2021
- Competitive rental and lease terms for a brand new facility   

The facility is located on Kiora Crescent within Yennora’s industrial precinct, with close proximity to major arterial roads, public transport and Yennora Distribution Centre.

The opportunity offers tenants the chance to secure space in one of Western Sydney’s most tightly held industrial locations. 

For further information please contact the exclusive agents, Elijah Shakir or Michael O'Neill from CBRE.

* approx

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A prominent industrial location occupied by a variety of users of both a local and regional nature. Centrally located providing excellent access to M4, M7 and the M5 Motorways.

- 2,000sqm* Building Area
- Internal clearance of up to 12m*
- Two (2) overhead gantry cranes
- Accessible via four (4) container height roller doors
- Exclusive yard area for truck manoeuvrability
- Bathroom amenities available 
- Ample parking available
- Fully sprinklered facility 
- Zoned IN1 General Industrial 
- Available with 1 months' notice

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact either of the exclusive agents listed.
